title: S12 Ep26: Children Of The Paranormal
itunes:title: Children Of The Paranormal
description:
Beyond The Darkness welcomes Clinical Psychologist/Paranormal Investigator Chelle Taylor in to talk about children who have had paranormal experiences, how they deal with it, how parents should help them through it, and some of the terrifying things that have happened as a result of exposure to the paranormal.

Chelle Taylor: https://www.facebook.com/paranormalmentalhealthconsultant
